OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776942175
OL,3,CChelsea sack Liam Rosenior after five
OL,4,Cconsecutive Premier League defeats
OL,6,FLiam Rosenior has been sacked by
OL,7,FChelsea following five consecutive
OL,8,FPremier League defeats in which the
OL,9,Fteam has failed to score.
OL,11,FThe former Hull and Strasbourg boss
OL,12,Fsigned a six-and-a-half-year deal in
OL,13,FJanuary but lasted just 106 days,
OL,14,Fculminating in Tuesday's 3-0 defeat at
OL,15,FBrighton.
OL,17,FIt was their fifth straight league
OL,18,Floss without scoring for the first
OL,19,Ftime since 1912.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
