OL,3,CChelsea sack Liam Rosenior after five
OL,4,Cconsecutive Premier League defeats
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FRosenior started brightly, winning his
OL,12,Ffour league matches in charge and
OL,13,Fleading the team to the last-16 of the
OL,14,FChampions League.
OL,16,FHowever, recent form has left them
OL,17,Falmost certain to miss out on
OL,18,Fqualification for next season's
OL,19,Fcompetition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
