PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776942175
OL,3,CChelsea sack Liam Rosenior after five
OL,4,Cconsecutive Premier League defeats
OL,6,FFollowing talks among the hierarchy on
OL,7,FWednesday, the decision was taken to
OL,8,Flook for a new head coach ` with first-
OL,9,Fteam coach and former under-21s boss
OL,10,FCalum McFarlane stepping in until the
OL,11,Fend of the campaign.
OL,13,FMcFarlane, who led the team for two
OL,14,Fmatches following the departure of
OL,15,FEnzo Maresca in January, will begin
OL,16,Fhis period in temporary charge with
OL,17,FSunday's FA Cup semi-final against
OL,18,FLeeds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
