OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776942175
OL,3,CChelsea sack Liam Rosenior after five
OL,4,Cconsecutive Premier League defeats
OL,6,FA club statement read: "Chelsea
OL,7,FFootball Club has today parted company
OL,8,Fwith Head Coach Liam Rosenior.
OL,10,F"On behalf of everyone at Chelsea FC,
OL,11,Fwe would like to place on record our
OL,12,Fgratitude to Liam and his staff for
OL,13,Fall their efforts during their time
OL,14,Fwith the Club.
OL,16,F"Liam has always conducted himself
OL,17,Fwith the highest integrity and
OL,18,Fprofessionalism following his
OL,19,Fappointment midway through the season.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776942175
OL,3,CChelsea sack Liam Rosenior after five
OL,4,Cconsecutive Premier League defeats
OL,6,F"This has not been a decision the Club
OL,7,Fhas taken lightly, however recent
OL,8,Fresults and performances have fallen
OL,9,Fbelow the necessary standards with
OL,10,Fstill so much more to play for this
OL,11,Fseason. Everyone at Chelsea FC wishes
OL,12,FLiam every success in the future.
OL,14,F"Calum McFarlane will take charge of
OL,15,Fthe team as Interim Head Coach until
OL,16,Fthe end of the season with support
OL,17,Ffrom existing Club backroom staff, as
OL,18,Fwe strive to achieve European
OL,19,Fqualification and progress in the FA
OL,20,FCup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776942175
OL,3,CChelsea sack Liam Rosenior after five
OL,4,Cconsecutive Premier League defeats
OL,6,F"As the Club works to bring stability
OL,7,Fto the Head Coach position, we will
OL,8,Fundertake a process of self-reflection
OL,9,Fto make the right long-term
OL,10,Fappointment."
OL,12,FIt's understood the club are not in
OL,13,Factive discussions with candidates and
OL,14,Fintend to take their time over their
OL,15,Fnext appointment, with no decision
OL,16,Fexpected before the end of the season.
OL,18,FChelsea's collapse under Rosenior
OL,19,Fbegan with a 5-2 hammering away to
OL,20,FParis St Germain on March 11 and from
OL,21,Fthere the rot set in.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776942175
OL,3,CChelsea sack Liam Rosenior after five
OL,4,Cconsecutive Premier League defeats
OL,6,FThe team has since plummeted down the
OL,7,Fleague table, having not picked up a
OL,8,Fpoint since beating Aston Villa on
OL,9,FMarch 4.
OL,11,FThey were beaten comfortably at the
OL,12,FAmex Stadium on Tuesday in what was
OL,13,Fwidely considered to have been their
OL,14,Fworst performance of the season.
OL,16,FDuring the match, Rosenior was for the
OL,17,Ffirst time subjected directly to
OL,18,Fchants from supporters calling for him
OL,19,Fto leave, while there were also the
OL,20,Fnow-customary demands for owners
OL,21,FBlueCo to sell up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
